<%= render "shared/header" %>
<h1 class="Lindex-title">About</h1>

<div class="about">
    <h2 class="sub-header">Introduction</h2>
    <p>Think you know football? Prove it!</p>
    <p><strong>Footy Predict</strong> is where you and your friends compete to predict football match results — and earn points for accuracy.</p>

    <ul>
        <li>🔮 Predict upcoming fixtures</li>
        <li>📈 Track your scores and rankings</li>
        <li>🏆 Battle for bragging rights each week</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Whether you're a casual fan or a stats-obsessed tactician, Footy Predict makes every match even more exciting.</p>
    <p>Predictions are currently limited to the Premier League, with plans to expand to other leagues and competitions in the future.</p>
    <p><strong>Ready to play? Create your account and make your picks!</strong></p>

    <h2 class="sub-header">Rules</h2>
    <p>The goal of the game is simple: predict the exact scores for each match.</p>
    <ul>
        <li>✅ 3 points for predicting the exact score</li>
        <li>⚖️ 1 point for predicting the correct outcome (win/loss/draw)</li>
        <li>❌ 0 points if your prediction is completely off</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Make smart picks and climb the leaderboard!</p>
</div>

